00:15:47.920 --> 00:15:50.560
and these are again as we
have discussed, plexuses are

00:15:50.560 --> 00:15:54.640
groups of nerves,
they contain both sympathetic,

00:15:54.640 --> 00:15:57.760
parasympathetic and sensory components.

