We only have sympathetic nerve endings

00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:30.720
and although we believe that
parasympathetic controls

00:16:30.720 --> 00:16:33.840
everything within the viscera,
we have discussed this before

00:16:33.840 --> 00:16:38.000
through the vagus nerve
for the most part

00:16:38.000 --> 00:16:41.520
but there are no sympathetic nerve
endings in the tips of our fingers.

00:16:41.520 --> 00:16:44.400
Now how is that important?

00:16:44.400 --> 00:16:48.800
It's important from a Sahaj
point of view because when

00:16:48.800 --> 00:16:54.480
the inner energy rises and it
crosses this energy center,

00:16:54.480 --> 00:16:58.240
the fifth energy center
within the central channel,

00:16:58.960 --> 00:17:01.600
through mechanisms that are
physiologically very difficult

00:17:01.600 --> 00:17:05.120
to appreciate, not yet,
I mean human science

00:17:05.120 --> 00:17:07.920
has not reached that stage
but probably one day will,

00:17:07.920 --> 00:17:15.680
however it allows us
to feel reality

00:17:15.680 --> 00:17:21.120
beyond the cognitive perception.

00:17:21.120 --> 00:17:24.560
And that is we can feel what
are called as vibrations,

00:17:24.560 --> 00:17:30.320
this cool breeze that does blow
through the tips of our fingers.

00:17:31.600 --> 00:17:33.280
Now let's put it all together.

00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:40.000
The energy rises through the central channel
which is parasympathetic.

00:17:40.000 --> 00:17:42.640
It is not sympathetic,
it is parasympathetic.

