However the ability to feel
the rising of this energy

00:17:47.680 --> 00:17:51.800
and the consequence
of that rising

00:17:51.800 --> 00:17:55.600
is felt through
the tips of our fingers

00:17:55.600 --> 00:17:57.920
which is sympathetic.

00:17:57.920 --> 00:18:01.520
And therefore it is at the
level of this energy center

00:18:01.520 --> 00:18:05.280
because of these two plexuses,
the brachial plexus

00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:08.480
and the cervical plexus but
predominantly the brachial plexus

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:14.480
which innervates our hands
and the nerves in our hands,

00:18:14.480 --> 00:18:20.880
