That you exist as part of a larger system,
of a larger reality that transcends you.

00:18:57.360 --> 00:19:02.560
And this is the beginning of what is called
collective consciousness.

00:19:02.560 --> 00:19:06.160
So we have individual
consciousness: I am breathing,

00:19:06.160 --> 00:19:09.280
I am seeing you, I am hearing
you, you are seeing me,

00:19:09.280 --> 00:19:11.840
so that is our individual consciousness.

00:19:11.840 --> 00:19:15.440
But when this inner energy
rises, it is only through

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:18.960
the awakening of this energy center

00:19:18.960 --> 00:19:23.680
that allows us to feel
through the sympathetic system

00:19:23.680 --> 00:19:28.000
what is actually happening within
the parasympathetic system.

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:29.600
So let me repeat that.

00:19:29.600 --> 00:19:35.520
These nerves at the tips of our fingers
do not have parasympathetic endings.

00:19:35.520 --> 00:19:38.480
So what is otherwise happening
within the parasympathetic,

00:19:38.480 --> 00:19:41.120
we would have no ability to know.

00:19:41.120 --> 00:19:46.640
It is only because of this
energy center that we can feel

00:19:46.640 --> 00:19:49.840
this sensation in our hands -
what is happening

00:19:49.840 --> 00:19:51.840
within the parasympathetic nervous system.

00:19:51.840 --> 00:19:55.840
And which is why the founder
of this system of meditation,

00:19:55.840 --> 00:19:59.840
Shri Mataji, always used to
say that in order to feel

00:19:59.840 --> 00:20:03.920
This cool breeze,
what She called vibrations,

00:20:03.920 --> 00:20:07.840
you need to have this energy center
that is in a very good condition,

00:20:07.840 --> 00:20:10.480
that is in a healthy condition
and therefore it is very important

00:20:10.480 --> 00:20:15.440
to keep this center
in a great working condition

00:20:15.440 --> 00:20:16.960
so that you can feel it.

00:20:16.960 --> 00:20:26.560
It is a bit complex,
but that is how we begin to comprehend

00:20:26.560 --> 00:20:31.920
and to experience
collective consciousness.

00:20:31.920 --> 00:20:36.560
Well, Dr. Ashish, every single discussion with you
has been so much interesting.

00:20:36.560 --> 00:20:39.360
We have learnt a lot with you
and I do want to once again

00:20:39.360 --> 00:20:40.720
thank you for your time today

00:20:40.720 --> 00:20:43.760
and we look forward to talking
to you on the next episode

00:20:43.760 --> 00:20:45.280
about the next energy center.

00:20:45.280 --> 00:20:46.560
Thanks once again.

00:20:46.560 --> 00:20:48.360
Thank you again.

00:20:48.880 --> 00:20:54.480
And we would encourage our viewers to follow
the meditation video that is going to be guided

00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:59.120
by the founder of this meditation and we wish you
all the very best in your experiment

00:20:59.120 --> 00:21:02.920
and this experience with Sahaj meditation.

00:21:02.920 --> 00:21:03.960
Thank you.

00:21:09.200 --> 00:21:13.040
Shri Mataji: Now we come to the other
center of Vishuddhi chakra.

00:21:13.040 --> 00:21:17.760
This is the
most important in the sense

00:21:17.760 --> 00:21:23.920
that it ends all your evolution as far as
human life is concerned.

00:21:23.920 --> 00:21:26.400
This has got sixteen petals.

00:21:26.400 --> 00:21:30.960
Outside in the gross it
manifests the cervical plexus

00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:34.400
and controls your ear, nose, throat, muscles,

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:37.600
your eyes and your face.

00:21:37.600 --> 00:21:46.720
Also it controls the first bone and all the bones
that go up to the cranial bones.

00:21:46.720 --> 00:21:55.120
It is the center of your responsibility
by which you feel responsibility.

00:21:55.120 --> 00:22:01.280
But when this center is awakened,
the greater center represents them here,

00:22:01.280 --> 00:22:06.400
because all these centers are represented again
in a bigger way in the brain.

00:22:06.400 --> 00:22:12.800
So this center when it is awakened,
which is a bigger, larger center of this,

00:22:12.800 --> 00:22:15.040
you become collectively conscious.

00:22:15.040 --> 00:22:17.536
This is the center of collectivity.

00:22:26.560 --> 00:22:29.920
Keep your eyes closed.

00:22:29.920 --> 00:22:34.800
First of all, please put your right hand
on your heart.

00:22:34.800 --> 00:22:38.800
All the time the left hand is towards Me.

00:22:38.800 --> 00:22:49.120
Now, here you have to say in your heart,
with all sincerity, Mother, am I the Spirit?

00:22:49.120 --> 00:22:51.760
Ask the question three times
in your heart.

00:22:51.760 --> 00:22:55.870
This is a very fundamental question.

00:23:12.960 --> 00:23:21.120
Now bring the right hand
on to the left hand side of your stomach,

00:23:21.120 --> 00:23:25.040
in the upper part.

00:23:25.040 --> 00:23:26.400
Here press it.

00:23:26.400 --> 00:23:34.880
Now this is the center of your mastery,
your guidance, your guru Tattva, as they say.

00:23:34.880 --> 00:23:39.280
So ask a question,
Mother, am I my own master?

00:23:39.280 --> 00:23:41.600
This is the question to be asked
three times.

00:23:41.600 --> 00:23:47.431
Mother, am I my own master?

00:23:59.200 --> 00:24:07.360
Now bring your right hand down below
in the lower part of the abdomen.

00:24:07.360 --> 00:24:15.040
Now this is the center from which
all the Divine work is done,

00:24:15.040 --> 00:24:17.840
all the pure work is done.

00:24:17.840 --> 00:24:22.960
So to ask six times,
because this center has got six petals,

00:24:22.960 --> 00:24:28.640
Mother, please give me pure knowledge.

00:24:28.640 --> 00:24:31.840
Six times you just ask.

00:24:31.840 --> 00:24:37.071
As a result of this asking
the Kundalini starts getting awakened.

00:24:47.951 --> 00:24:52.720
Now to help the Kundalini to rise
you have to cooperate with Her.

00:24:52.720 --> 00:24:56.880
So please put your right hand
on the left hand side

00:24:56.880 --> 00:25:06.080
in the upper part of your abdomen
and press it on the stomach.

00:25:06.080 --> 00:25:11.760
Now here you have to say
with full confidence,

00:25:11.760 --> 00:25:18.480
to help the Kundalini to rise,
Mother, I am my own master.

00:25:18.480 --> 00:25:20.720
This you have to say ten times.

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:23.760
These are the ten commandments
which you have to say,

00:25:23.760 --> 00:25:28.495
that Mother, I am my own master.

00:26:04.880 --> 00:26:11.280
Now, ten times with full confidence.

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:21.360
Now please raise your right hand
to your heart.

00:26:21.360 --> 00:26:28.240
Now here you have to say,
again with full confidence,

00:26:28.240 --> 00:26:30.640
Mother, I am the Spirit.

00:26:30.640 --> 00:26:33.040
This is the truth, you are the Spirit.

00:26:33.040 --> 00:26:38.480
But you have to say with full confidence,
Mother, I am the Spirit.

00:26:39.440 --> 00:26:43.236
This you have to say twelve times.

00:27:10.720 --> 00:27:17.840
Now one has to know
that God Almighty is the ocean of love.

00:27:17.840 --> 00:27:22.720
But above all He is the ocean
of forgiveness.

00:27:22.720 --> 00:27:24.560
So He forgives.

00:27:24.560 --> 00:27:27.200
Whatever wrong you do He forgives.

00:27:27.200 --> 00:27:34.880
So don't feel guilty
and put your right hand across

00:27:34.880 --> 00:27:43.360
on the left hand side in the corner
which is made by your neck and your shoulder.

00:27:43.360 --> 00:27:47.520
Now here you have to say
again with full confidence,

00:27:47.520 --> 00:27:51.280
sixteen times, Mother, I am not guilty.

00:27:51.280 --> 00:27:54.560
Please say it, Mother, I am not guilty.

00:27:54.560 --> 00:27:58.000
Sixteen times.

00:27:58.000 --> 00:28:01.363
I am not guilty at all.

00:28:01.363 --> 00:28:09.499
Please say it.

00:28:39.520 --> 00:28:49.040
Now raise your hand across on your forehead
and it's a very important center.

00:28:49.040 --> 00:28:59.840
Here you have to say from your heart,
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:28:59.840 --> 00:29:02.080
Please say it from your heart.

00:29:02.080 --> 00:29:04.160
How many times is not the point.

00:29:04.160 --> 00:29:08.560
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:29:08.560 --> 00:29:12.240
Now some would say
that it's very difficult to forgive.

00:29:12.240 --> 00:29:18.160
But it's a myth
that we do not forgive or we forgive.

00:29:18.160 --> 00:29:21.040
We do not do anything
in both the cases.

00:29:21.040 --> 00:29:25.040
But if we don't forgive
then we play into wrong hands.

00:29:25.040 --> 00:29:32.028
So please say from your heart,
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:29:39.440 --> 00:29:46.640
Now please take your hand on the back agnya,
the same center, on the back side of your head

00:29:46.640 --> 00:29:51.680
and allow your head to rest on it
and push it back a little bit.

00:29:52.480 --> 00:29:59.040
Now here you have to say
for your satisfaction,

00:29:59.040 --> 00:30:05.520
because you always feel guilty,
that, O Divine, if I have done anything wrong,

00:30:05.520 --> 00:30:08.830
please forgive me.

00:30:14.640 --> 00:30:23.040
Please forgive me, from your heart.

00:30:23.040 --> 00:30:29.600
Stretch your hand fully
and put your center of your palm

00:30:29.600 --> 00:30:38.400
on top of the fontanel bone area,
which was a very soft bone in your childhood.

00:30:38.400 --> 00:30:39.600
Press it hard.

00:30:39.600 --> 00:30:43.120
Press hard your scalp.

00:30:43.120 --> 00:30:49.360
Now you have to move it seven times
saying one thing, which you have to ask for,

00:30:49.360 --> 00:30:54.640
Mother, please give us My Self-realization,
because I cannot force on you.

00:30:54.640 --> 00:30:57.360
So you have to ask for it.

00:30:57.360 --> 00:31:05.920
Seven times press it hard
and move it seven times very hard.

00:31:05.920 --> 00:31:10.214
Slowly saying that.
